dct_title_s: Map illustrating the system of parcs, the domestic relations of the Great Plains, the North American Andes, and the Pacific maritime
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. From: Gilpin, William. Mission of the North American people, geographical, social and political. Philadelphia : J.B. Lippincott & Co., 1874. Shows existing railroad lines and lands covered by Indian treaties.
